\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $L=Q_{C}-Q_{F}=mc\left(T_{1}-T_{2}\right)-mcT_{F}\ln\frac{T_{1}}{T_{2}}$
\end_inset

 in valore assoluto 
\end_layout

